{"tid":1851272,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個情況可唔可以享有有薪病假","createTime":"2020-01-30T03:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T15:39:37.000Z","uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e79a37185dc736242f28183bc909b18e53949216","tid":1851272,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:23:18.000Z","msg":"中耳炎搞到半邊頭、喉嚨、牙骹都好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴日睇開嘅醫生冇開<br />\n所以求其睇咗另一個醫生<br />\n拎咗29/1 - 30/1 兩日假<br />\n今日仍然好唔掂<br />\n想去返睇開嘅醫生度睇多次<br />\n順便攞埋31/1 - 1/2 兩日假<br />\n<br />\n咁樣可唔可以當連續4日請假？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d359e516ba686f17520dcf54799fe5f30fa760c3","tid":1851272,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"問 2.\t如 何 累 積 有 薪 病 假 日 ？<br />\n答 2.\t<br />\n僱 員 按 連 續 性 合 約 受僱，在最初受僱的12個月內每服務滿1個月，便可累積2天有薪病假；之後每服務滿1個月可累積4天。有薪病假可在整個受僱期間持續累積，但在任何時間不得超過120天。"},{"pid":"7b9befc7cfbdd2168099b2c737d0a9a377665778","tid":1851272,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d359e516ba686f17520dcf54799fe5f30fa760c3","tid":1851272,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"問 2.\t如 何 累 積 有 薪 病 假 日 ？<br />\n答 2.\t<br />\n僱 員 按 連 續 性 合 約 受僱，在最初受僱的12個月內每服務滿1個月，便可累積2天有薪病假；之後每服務滿1個月可累積4天。有薪病假可在整個受僱期間持續累積，但在任何時間不得超過120天。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:34:45.000Z","msg":"thx Wang<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我想知呢個情況放唔放到有薪病假呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公司仆街到叫我請假期間返嚟處理兩個鐘頭緊急嘢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />DLLM"},{"pid":"7af39b13104acd953e7821b0094de73d6a9e16a6","tid":1851272,"uid":71166,"like